Usage: chain [-h] [-p nprocs] [-c nchars] [-s sleeptime] [-i niters] < textfile

 Option				Meaning
-p				Number of processes [default 4]
-c				Number of characters read into the buffer [default 80]
-s				Time to sleep in each iteration [default 3s]
-i				Number of iterations in the loop
< textfile			File containing text to be read through stdin
